-- Hartford Hires High for Group Benefits, Reporting to Concannon
-- B y   E l i z a b e t h   B u n n
-- 2013-03-04T15:18:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-04/hartford-hires-high-for-group-benefits-reporting-to-concannon.html
Hartford Financial Services Group
Inc. (HIG) , the insurer that restated third-quarter results last week,
named Lori High chief sales and marketing officer for the group
benefits unit.  High previously worked in group insurance at  Prudential
Financial Inc. (PRU)  and will report to Mike Concannon, executive vice
president of group benefits, according to a Business Wire
statement today from Hartford, which is based in the Connecticut
city of the same name.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elizabeth Bunn in New York at 
 ebunn1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  